    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "There is hot water in a thermos and I make an Aeropress, Jordan a Rooibos tea, and go down to the deck. We were thinking about trying to go for a sail on one of the small boats, but there is a proper gale blowing this morning and it doesn’t feel like it would be a relaxing time. ",
            "link": null
          },
